		<property name="note">
			<value>An ambience (looping) event for when our player is in the Forest environment. This event uses 2 parameters, ForestTime and BirdIntensity.

ForestTime:
0 - Morning
1 - Evening
2 - Night

BirdIntensity:
0 -&gt; no birds chirping
1 -&gt; birds awake and flying
(volume and spawn rate changes depening on the ForestTime - the later it is, the less birds you will hear and vice versa.)</value>
		</property>
